20was%20primarily%20skewed%20towards%20professionals%20in%20the%202-5%20years%20and%205-7%20years%20experience%20bracket.%20These%20two%20categories%20have%20even%20historically%20favoured%20because%20of%20their%20adaptability%20and%20lower%20cost%20to%20organisations%20compared%20to%20more%20senior%20age%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Bprofessionals%20in%20these%20brackets%20have%20relevant%20skills%20and%20practical%20experience%2C%20giving%20them%20an%20edge%20over%20freshers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20number%20of%20data%20jobs%20have%20dropped%2C%20Bengaluru%20continues%20to%20hold%20the%20largest%20share%2C%20but%20the%20country's%20tech%20capital%20is%20reaching%20a%20saturation%20point.%20According%20to%20the%20jobs%20report%2C%20companies%20are%20moving%20to%20other%20locations%2C%20such%20as%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Hyderabad%20and%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20massive%20digital%20transformation%20supporting%20business%20operations%20globally%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20considerable%20push%20towards%20embracing%20data-driven%20decisions%20to%20achieve%20more%20efficient%20business%20operations.%20This%20year's%20report%20has%20sprung%20some%20surprises%20-%20but%20once%20economies%20rebound%2C%20we%20can%20expect%20data%20science%20and%20analytics%20jobs%20in%20India%20to%20grow%20further%20and%20open%20up%20more%20unique%20job%20profiles%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Great%20Learning%20co-founder%20Hari%20Krishnan%20Nair.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694607240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F3occ0n3_quiet-hiring_625x300_27_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fjobs%2Fthese-are-the-most-in-demand-positions-in-india-as-per-jobs-report-4386367%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20jobs%20report%20painted%20a%20grim%20picture%20for%20senior-level%20professionals%2C%20saying%20there%20is%20a