urce%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3Eover%204%2C300%2Co00%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20about%2020%25%20a%20year%2C%20since%20Warren%20Buffett%20took%20over%20as%20CEO%20in%201965.%20Buffett%20and%20his%20business%20partner%2C%20Charlie%20Munger%2C%20have%20achieved%20that%20phenomenal%20gain%20for%20three%20clear%20reasons%2C%20Howard%20Marks%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20ingredients%20of%20Warren's%20and%20Charlie's%20great%20performance%20are%20simple%3A%20(a)%20a%20lot%20of%20investments%20in%20which%20they%20did%20decently%2C%20(b)%20a%20relatively%20small%20number%20of%20big%20winners%20that%20they%20invested%20in%20heavily%20and%20held%20for%20decades%2C%20and%20(c)%20relatively%20few%20big%20losers%2C%26quot%3B%20Marks%20wrote%20in%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oaktreecapital.com%2Finsights%2Fmemo%2Ffewer-losers-or-more-winners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elatest%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20published%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20investor%20and%20co-chairman%20of%20Oaktree%20Capital%20Management%20nodded%20to%20Buffett's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-annual-shareholder-letter-coke-amex-buybacks-taxes-earnings-2023-2%5C%22%3Eshareholder%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Berkshire%20chief%20attributed%20his%20company's%20success%20to%20%26quot%3Ba%20dozen%20truly%20good%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20about%20one%20every%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20singled%20out%20his%20bets%20on%20Coca-Cola%20and%20American%20Express%20as%20examples.%20He%20invested%20about%20%241.3%20billion%20in%20each%20stock%20in%20the%20mid-1990s.%20Those%20positions%20are%20each%20worth%20about%20%2425%20billion%20today%2C%20and%20together%20they%20yield%20over%20%241%20billion%20in%20dividends%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20weeds%20wither%20away%20in%20significance%20as%20the%20flowers%20bloom%2C%26