in%20July%202022%20when%20he%20visited%20the%20Greek%20island%20of%20Mykonos.%3Cp%3EMEGA%2FGC%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWalter%20Isaacson's%20biography%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20shines%20new%20light%20on%20the%20world's%20richest%20person.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20once%20took%20a%20safari%20during%20a%20vacation%20to%20his%20native%20South%20Africa%20but%20contracted%20malaria.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20Musk%20was%20in%20hospital%2C%20colleagues%20found%20he'd%20taken%20out%20a%20%24100%20million%20life%20insurance%20policy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20biography%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20might%20explain%20one%20reason%20why%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-net-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20world's%20richest%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%20seems%20to%20dislike%20vacations%3A%20he%20contracted%20malaria%20while%20on%20safari%20in%20South%20Africa%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalter%20Isaacson%2C%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musks-biographer-musk-multiple-personalities-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiography%20of%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20published%20this%20week%2C%20was%20given%20access%20to%20the%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20CEO%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20One%20chapter%20details%20his%20near-death%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20ousted%20as%20CEO%20of%20PayPal%20by%20Peter%20Thiel%20in%20October%202000%2C%20Musk%20took%20what%20Isaacson%20said%20was%20his%20first%20real%20vacation%20from%20work%2C%20first%20traveling%20to%20Brazil%20to%20visit%20his%20cousin%20and%20then%20on%20to%20his%20native%20South%20Africa%20for%20a%20wedding.%20It%20was%20Musk's%20first%20time%20back%20since%20leaving%20for%20Canada%20aged%2017%2C%20Isaacson%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20time%20with%20his%20family%20in%20Pretoria%2C%20Musk%20and%20his%20then-wife%20Justine%20Musk%20went%20t