%20of%20performing%20special%20missions%20as%20well%20as%20disaster%20response%20and%20maritime%20patrol%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20mega%20deal%20was%20finalised%20last%20year%2C%20Airbus%20said%20the%20C295%20programme%20will%20see%20the%20company%20bring%20its%20complete%20bouquet%20of%20world-class%20aircraft%20manufacturing%20and%20servicing%20to%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20its%20industrial%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20first%20C295%20aircraft%20built%20for%20India%20successfully%20completed%20its%20maiden%20flight%20in%20Seville.%20The%20second%20one%20is%20in%20the%20final%20assembly%20at%20the%20Seville%20facility%20and%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20delivered%20to%20the%20IAF%20in%20May%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20mega%20deal%20was%20finalised%2C%20Airbus%20said%20the%20C295%20programme%20will%20see%20the%20company%20bring%20its%20complete%20bouquet%20of%20world-class%20aircraft%20manufacturing%20and%20servicing%20to%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20its%20industrial%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20pilots%20from%20the%20IAF%20and%2020%20technicians%20have%20already%20undergone%20extensive%20training%20at%20the%20Seville%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20assembly%20line%20for%20the%20C295%20aircraft%20in%20Vadodara%20is%20set%20to%20be%20operational%20in%20November%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20IAF%20will%20be%20the%20world's%20largest%20operator%20of%20the%20C295.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694602980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fcr9sbqdk_iaf-c295-1200_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-force-receives-keys-of-first-c295-tactical-airlifter-from-airbus-4385980%22%2C%22summary%22%3A