20fatal%20for%20the%20first%20democratically%20elected%20socialist%20government%20of%20Chile.%20This%20coup%20was%20successful%2C%20mainly%20on%20account%20of%20the%20absolute%20unity%20achieved%20between%20all%20branches%20of%20the%20Chilean%20Armed%20Forces%20and%20active%20support%20from%20the%20Nixon%20administration%20in%20the%20US%20that%20worked%20towards%20creating%20favourable%20conditions%20for%20the%20anti-Allende%20coup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20232px)%2085vw%2C%20232px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13152718%2FSalvador_Allende_Gossens--232x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22232%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13152718%2FSalvador_Allende_Gossens--232x300.jpg%20232w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13152718%2FSalvador_Allende_Gossens-.jpg%20325w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672849%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChile%E2%80%99s%20former%20President%20Salvador%20Allende%20Credit%3A%20Biblioteca%20del%20Congreso%20Nacional%20de%20Chile%2C%20CC%20BY%203.0%20CL%2F%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20would%20become%20iconic%20images%20of%20the%20coup%2C%20the%20Chilean%20Air%20Force%20bombed%20La%20Moneda%20%E2%80%93%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20White%20House.%20It%20became%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20brutality%20with%20which%20an%20elected%20government%20was%20deposed%2C%20thus%20leading%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Farchives%2Ffrom-the-hindu-archives-september-13-1973-ousted-chilean-president-commits-suicide%2Farticle67298607.ece%5C%22%3Edeath-by-suicide%20of%20President%20Allende%3C%2Fa%3E%20inside%20the%20presidential%20palace%20in%20the%20capital%20Santiago%20on%20that%20fateful%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20fatalities%20in%20the%20battle%20during%20the%20coup%20might%20have%20been%20relatively%20small%2C%20the%20Chilean%20security%20forces%20sustained%20casualties%20in%20the%20three%20following%20months%20as%20a%20result%20of%20continued%20resistance%20from%20pro-democracy%20forces.%20In%20the%20months%20after%20the%20coup%20d%E2%80%99%C3%A9tat%2C%20the%20military%20killed%20thousands%20of%20Chilean%20left-wing%20activists%2C%20both%20real%20and%20suspected%2C%20or%20forced%20their%20%E2%80%9Cdisappearance%E2%80%9D.%20The%20junta%20government%20arrested%20some%20130%2C000%20people%20in%20a%20three-year%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coup%20went%20on%20to%20inspire%20military%20takeovers%20across%20Latin%20America%20%E2%80%93%20but%20also%20galvanised%20the%20human%20rights%20movement.%20The%20brazen%20support%20for%20the%20coup%20brought%20the%20focus%20on%20to%20the%20dark%20activities%20of%20the%20CIA%20in%20subverting%20democracies%2C%20in%20cahoots%20with%20its%20allies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20UK%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20decades%20on%2C%20the%20wounds%20left%20in%20Chilean%20society%20by%20the%20coup%20are%20still%20very%20much%20open.%20Justice%20is%20a%20long%20way%20from%20being%20served%2C%20secrets%20remain%20untold%2C%20and%20the%20bodies%20of%20many%20of%20the%20victims%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChile%E2%80%99s%20march%20back%20to%20democracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2050%20years%20since%2C%20Chile%20has%20traversed%20the%20full%20road%20to%20recovery.%20The%20internationally%20supported%201989%20Chilean%20constitutional%20referendum%20held%20under%20the%20military%20junta%20led%20to%20the%20peaceful%20Chilean%20transition%20back%20to%20democracy.%20Attempts%20were%20made%20to%20bring%20the%20top%20leadership%2C%20including%20General%20Augusto%20Pinochet%2C%20to%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20Chile.%20By%20the%20time%20of%20his%20death%20in%202006%2C%20about%20300%20criminal%20charges%20were%20still%20pending%20against%20him%20in%20Chile%20for%20numerous%20human%20rights%20violations%20during%20his%2017-year%20rule%2C%20as%20well%20as%20tax%20evasion%20and%20embezzlement%20during%20and%20after%20his%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sign%20of%20how%20advanced%20Chilean%20democracy%20has%20really%20become%2C%20it%20became%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20pass%20a%20law%20on%20neuro-rights%20(fundamental%20normative%20rules%20for%20the%20protection%20and%20preservation%20of%20the%20human%20brain%20and%20mind)%20in%202021%2C%20thus%20proving%20that%20it%20is%20a%20capable%2021st%20century%20democracy.%20Chile%20underwent%20two%20recent%20attempts%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20new%2C%20more%20advanced%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20coup%2C%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20current%20President%20Gabriel%20Boric%2C%20along%20with%20all%20four%20living%20former%20presidents%20%E2%80%94%20Eduardo%20Frei%20Ruiz-Tagle%2C%20Ricardo%20Lagos%2C%20Michelle%20Bachelet%2C%20and%20Sebastian%20Pi%C3%B1era%20%E2%80%94%20signed%20a%20declaration%20titled%20%E2%80%98Compromise%20with%20Democracy%E2%80%99.%20The%C2%A0%20declaration%20states%20that%20the%20signatories%20should%20%E2%80%9Cconfront%20the%20challenges%20of%20democracy%20with%20more%20democracy%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20they%20should%20%E2%80%9Cdefend%20and%20promote%20human%20rights%E2%80%9D.%20The%20right-wing%20opposition%20in%20Chile%20called%20the%20declaration%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%E2%80%9D%20and%20refused%20to%20sign%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coup%E2%80%99s%20lasting%20legacy%20around%20the%20world%20has%20been%20defined%20mostly%20by%20the%20international%20backlash%20to%20its%20shocking%20cruelty.%20It%20galvanised%20the%20human%20rights%20movement%20globally%2C%20and%20more%20specifically%20in%20Latin%20America.%20The%20US%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20shocked%20politicians%20such%20as%20liberal%20US%20Senator%20Frank%20F.%20Church%2C%20who%20oversaw%20the%20first%20congressional%20hearings%20on%20the%20CIA%E2%80%99s%20covert%20activities%20that%20ultimately%20led%20to%20constraints%20on%20its%20future%20operations%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20martyrdom%20of%20Salvador%20Allende%20and%20his%20experiment%20in%20democratic%20socialism%20continues%20to%20inspire%20generations%20of%20progressive%20social%20and%20political%20activists%20around%20the%20world%20to%20build%20and%20strengthen%20robust%20constitutional%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVinay%20N.%20Bhushan%20worked%20as%20a%20consultant%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20and%20Bhargava%20Reddy%20works%20for%20APAC%20Assistance.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694601013000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13152517%2FGolpe_de_Estado_1973.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Flessons-from-chiles-1973-coup%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Half%20a%20century%20later%2C%20the%20events%20of%20that%20fateful%20day%20continue%20to%20send%20shockwaves%20across%20generations.%20The%20coup%20continues%20to%20inspire%20popular%20struggles%20to%20install%20and%20reinforce%20democratic%20constitutional%20orders%20in%20the%20Global%20South.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Flessons-from-chiles-1973-coup%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20upcoming%20movies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694601000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103634030%2Cimgsize-35298.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fshah-rukh-khans-upcoming-movies%2Fphotostory%2F103634030.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.