hildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Sanskrit%20is%20not%20taught%20in%20Devbhoomi%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20then%20where%20will%20it%20be%20taught%3F%26quot%3B%20Shadab%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%C2%A0%26quot%3BStudents%20should%20have%20knowledge%20of%20every%20language%20and%20culture.%20The%20education%20in%20madrassas%20should%20not%20be%20limited.%20Muslim%20children%20have%20the%20right%20to%20study%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20modernisation%C2%A0of%20madrassas'%20education%20system%2C%20Shams%20said%20the%20curriculum%20will%20be%20an%20amalgamation%20of%20scientific%20learning%20and%20Islamic%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Waqf%20Board%20in%20Uttarakhand%20has%20decided%20to%20implement%20the%20NCERT%20syllabus%20in%20the%20117%20Waqf%20Board%C2%A0madrassa%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20NCERT%20Syllabus%20includes%20Sanskrit%20also.%20When%20our%20children%20can%20learn%20Hindi%2C%20English%2C%20Math%2C%20Science%2C%20Physics%2C%20Chemistry%2C%20Biology%2C%20and%20Arabic%2C%20they%20can%20study%20Sanskrit%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Shams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20chief%20minister%20has%20assured%20us%20that%20any%20help%20needed%20to%20educate%20the%20children%2C%20the%20government%20is%20ready%20for%20it.%20They%20will%20also%20walk%20on%20the%20path%20of%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam.%20We%20are%20going%20ahead%20with%20positive%20vibes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E40-50%20madrassas%20approached%20seeking%20modernisation%3A%20Uttarakhand%20Waqf%20Board%20chairman%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Waqf%20Board%20chairman%20said%2040-50%20madrassas%20%26quot%3Bhave%20approached%20us%20seeking%20modernisation%20of%20their%20education%20system%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20done%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20four%20madrassas%20that%20were%20modernised%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20Haridwar%2C%20Udham%20Singh%20Nagar%20and%20Nainital%20districts%2C%26quot%3B%20Shams%20told%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BHave%20received%20positive%20response%20from%20students'%20parents%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20enthusiastic%20response%20of%20parents%20and%20guardians%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20revolution.%20We%20were%20expecting%20a%20stiff%20resistance%20from%20the%20Muslim%20families%2C%20especially%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20clerics%20to%20any%20attempt%20to%20modernise%20madrassa%20education%20in%20the%20state%2C%20but%20the%20situation%20is%20the%20opposite%2C%26quot%3B%20Shams%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20infrastructure%20required%20for%20this%20exercise%20is%20being%20created%20in%20the%20madrassas%20selected%20in%20the%20first%20phase%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20was%20in%20line%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20statement%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20see%20madrassa-going%20children%20with%20the%20Quran%20in%20one%20hand%20and%20a%20laptop%20in%20the%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20this%20exercise%20is%20completed%2C%20more%20districts%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20modernisation%20programme%2C%20he%20further%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESoon%20after%20taking%20over%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Waqf%20Board%20in%202022%2C%20Shams%20had%20pitched%20for%20providing%20modern%20education%20at%20madrassas%20and%20talked%20about%20the%20board's%20plans%20to%20impart%20the%20same%20education%20to%20madrassa%20students%20as%20those%20studying%20in%20other%20schools.%20The%20Uttarakhand%20Waqf%20Board%20runs%20103%20madrassas%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20agencies)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694599560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fhqouf2n_uttarakhand-waqf-board-chairman-shadab-shams_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fsanskrit-to-be-part-of-ncert-syllabus-in-uttarakhand-madrassas-4385479%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Uttarakhand%20Waqf%20Board%20will%20implement%20the%20NCERT%20syllabus%20in%20117%20madrassas%20across%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fsanskrit-to-be-part-of-ncert-syllabus-in-uttarakhand-madrassas-4385479%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fsanskrit-to-be-part-of-ncert-syllabus-in-uttarakhand-madrassas-4385479%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fsanskrit-to-be-part-of-ncert-syllabus-in-uttarakhand-madrassas-4385479%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Woman%20Accidentally%20Swallows%20Apple%20AirPod%20Mistaking%20It%20For%20Vitamin%20Pill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2052-year-old%20TikToker%20in%20the%20US%20has%20sparked%20laughter%20online%20after%20she%20revealed%20that%20she%20swallowed%20one%20of%20her%20husband's%20Apple%20AirPod%20Pro%2C%20mistaking%20them%20for%20vitamins%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F09%2F12%2Fi-accidentally-ate-an-airpod-with-no-choice-but-to-let-it-pass-naturally%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%20The%20unfortunate%20yet%20hilarious%20incident%20happened%20when%C2%A0Realtor%20Tanna%20Barker%20was%20out%20on%20a%20morning%20walk%20with%20her%20friend.%C2%A0Engrossed%20in%20the%20conversation%2C%20she%20went%20to%20take%20her%20vitamins%20and%20mistakenly%20swallowed%20her%20husband's%20left%20AirPod%20Pro%20with%20a%20drink%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwoman-accidentally-swallowed-an-airpod-instead-of-her-vitamins-2023-9%5C%22%3EInsider%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E''Halfway%20through%20my%20walk%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20my%20vitamins%2C%20so%20I%20put%20my%20vitamins%20in%2C%20took%20a%20drink%2C%20and%20was%20like%2C%20'Man%2C%20those%20are%20stuck.'%20So%20I%20guzzled%20my%20water%2C%20said%20goodbye%20to%20Kathleen%2C%20and%20went%20to%20go%20get%20my%20AirPod%20and%20my%20pills%20were%20in%20my%20hand%2C''%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E''I%20could%20feel%20it%20going%20down%20so%20slow%E2%80%A6I%20was%20just%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Oh%20my%20gosh%2C%20I%20cannot%20believe%20I%20just%20did%20that.%20I've%20got%20an%20AirPod%20inside%20me%20now%2C''%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20reached%20home%20and%20narrated%20the%20embarrasing%20mishap%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20he%20asked%20her%20not%20to%20tell%20anyone%20about%20it.%20However%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20share%20the%20incident%20with%20her%20TikTok%20followers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20video%20soon%20went%20viral%2C%20with%20many%20users%20being%20invested%20and%20fascinated%20by%20her%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20get%20it%20back%2C%20it%20will%20be%20an%20ipood.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20imagining%20your%20friend%20watching%20you%20casually%20eat%20your%20AirPod%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20person%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20ingesting%20the%20device%2C%20she%20reached%20out%20to%20numerous%20doctors%20and%20friends%20for%20guidance%20who%20advised%20her%20to%20let%20the%20AirPod%20pass%20through%20her%20system%20naturally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E''Almost%20all%20of%20them%20said%20to%20let%20it%20pass%20naturally%2C%20and%20it%20should%20be%20fine%20because%20the%20battery's%20encased.%20One%20of%20them%20asked%20if%20I%20had%20swallowed%20both%20%5BAirPods%2C%5D%20and%20I%20said%20no.%20And%20he%20said%2C%20'Well%2C%20that's%20good%20because%20it%20has%20the%20magnet%20in%20it%20and%20that%20could%20have%20caused%20an%20issue%2C''%20Mrs%20Barker%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20she%20posted%20a%20follow-up%20video%20informing%20her%20followers%20that%20the%20AirPod%20had%20exited%20her%20system%20safely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20hashtags%20%5Bon%20the%20original%20video%5D%20was%20%23ThisTooShallPass.%20And%20it%20has.%20It%20has%20been%20such%20an%20amazing%20experience%20and%20such%20a%20wild%20ride%2C%20and%20I%20am%20so%20grateful%20that%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20protect%20my%20mindset%2C%20''%20she%20said%20in%20the%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694599440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fct1blmo8_apple-airpods_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwoman-accidentally-swallows-apple-airpods-mistaking-it-for-vitamin-pill-4385768%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Engrossed%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20her%20friend%2C%20she%20went%20to%20take%20her%20vitamins%20and%20mistakenly%20swallowed%20her%20husband's%20left%20AirPod%20Pro%20with%20a%20drink.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwoman-accidentally-swallows-apple-airpods-mistaking-it-for-vitamin-pill-4385768%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwoman-accidentally-swallows-apple-airpods-mistaking-it-for-vitamin-pill-4385768%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwoman-accidentally-swallows-apple-airpods-mistaking-it-for-vitamin-pill-4385768%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20approves%2075L%20free%20LPG%20connections%20under%20Ujjwala%20scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694598940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103633093%2Cimgsize-51436.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fgovt-approves-75-lakh-free-lpg-connections-under-ujjwala-scheme%2Farticleshow%2F103633107.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20approved%20the%20allocation%20of%20Rs%201%2C650%20crore%20to%20oil%20m