ws%20had%20reported%20earlier%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20growing%20challenges%20for%20Apple%20in%20its%20biggest%20foreign%20market%20and%20global%20production%20base.%20Several%20agencies%20have%20begun%20instructing%20staff%20not%20to%20bring%20their%20iPhones%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20has%20not%20issued%20laws%20and%20regulations%20to%20ban%20the%20purchase%20of%20Apple%20or%20foreign%20brands'%20phones%2C%26quot%3B%20Mao%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20government%20attaches%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20importance%26quot%3B%20to%20security%20and%20that%20all%20companies%20operating%20in%20China%20need%20to%20abide%20by%20its%20laws%20and%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMao's%20comments%20about%20security%20incidents%20were%20slightly%20different%20in%20the%20official%20English%20translation%20of%20the%20news%20briefing.%20That%20translation%2C%20delivered%20simultaneously%20onsite%20by%20the%20ministry%2C%20omitted%20the%20reference%20to%20media%20%26quot%3Breports.%26quot%3B%20Foreign%20affairs%20ministry%20briefings%20are%20typically%20rigorously%20controlled%20and%20spokespeople's%20responses%20are%20usually%20scripted%20ahead%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20conference%20came%20just%20hours%20after%20Apple%20unveiled%20its%20latest%20model%20of%20the%20marquee%20device%2C%20the%20iPhone%2015.%20The%20company%20unveiled%20four%20new%20models%2C%20keeping%20pace%20with%20the%20past%20few%20generations%3A%20the%20iPhone%2015%2C%2015%20Plus%2C%2015%20Pro%20and%2015%20Pro%20Max.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Beijing%20goes%20ahead%20with%20an%20iPhone%20ban%2C%20the%20unprecedented%20blockade%20will%20be%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20years-long%20effort%20to%20root%20out%20foreign%20technology%20use%20in%20sensitive%20environments%2C%20coinciding%20with%20Beijing's%20effort%20to%20reduce%20its%20reliance%20on%20American%20software%20and%20circuitry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20threatens%20to%20erode%20Apple's%20position%20in%20a%20market%20that%20yields%20about%