0Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20dinner%20with%20personnel%20from%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20force%20said%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Arora%20has%20sought%20a%20list%20of%20personnel%20from%20each%20district%20-%20from%20constables%20to%20inspectors%20-%20who%20did%20an%20excellent%20job%20during%20the%20summit%20last%20weekend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20450%20personnel%2C%20who%2C%20along%20with%20Mr%20Arora%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20dinner%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam%2C%20which%20was%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20PM%20Modi%20will%20be%20recognising%20the%20efforts%20of%20people%20involved%20in%20a%20major%20achievement.%20In%20May%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20Parliament%20Building%2C%20he%20had%20felicitated%20the%20labourers%20involved%20in%20its%20construction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Sanjay%20Arora%20had%20also%20awarded%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Police's%20special%20commendation%20disc%20and%20certificate%20to%20some%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel%20for%20their%20contribution%20to%20the%20G20%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20announcing%20this%2C%20which%20was%20dated%20September%2011%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20smooth%2C%20professional%20and%20precise%20execution%20of%20the%20colossal%20G20%20arrangement%2C%20which%20saw%20participation%2C%20commitment%20and%20contribution%20from%20the%20entire%20rank%20and%20file%20of%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20was%20made%20possible%20only%20by%20the%20shared%20sense%20of%20pride%20and%20ownership%20in%20the%20overall%20objectives%20of%20the%20mega%20arrangement%20by%20every%20participant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20a%20difficult%20task%20on%20their%20hands%20both%20before%20and%20during%20the%20summit%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20largest%20congregation%20of%20world%20leaders%20in%20the%20country%20in%20recent%20memory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20security%20and%20secrecy%2C%20the%20Special%20Protection%20Group%20and%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel%20also%20used%20code%20words%20for%20the%20hotels%20where%20the%20leaders%20and%20their%20delegations%20were%20staying%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ITC%20Maurya%20Sheraton%2C%20where%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20staying%2C%20was%20code-named%20'Pandora'%20and%20'Samara'%20was%20the%20name%20for%20Shangri-La%2C%20where%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Akshata%20Murthy%2C%20were%20living%20during%20the%20summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECode%20words%20were%20also%20used%20for%20places%20that%20the%20leaders%20would%20visit.%20Rajghat%20was%20called%20'Rudpur'%20and%20Pragati%20Maidan%2C%20where%20the%20summit%20was%20held%2C%20was%20'Niketan'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694594100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4q9ci83g_delhi-police-g20-summit-security-650_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-done-pm-modis-dinner-plan-with-450-delhi-cops-4385469%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20bid%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20contributions%20of%20everyone%20who%20was%20part%20of%20making%20the%20G20%20Summit%20a%20success%20are%20recognised%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20dinner%20with%20personnel%20from%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-done-pm-modis-dinner-plan-with-450-delhi-cops-4385469%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-done-pm-modis-dinner-plan-with-450-delhi-cops-4385469%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F