ia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaran-johar-addresses-nepo-mafia-label-as-lakshya-makes-his-debut-in-kill%2Farticleshow%2F103629627.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IAF%20To%20Receive%20Its%20First%20C-295%20Transport%20Plane%20Today%3A%20Know%20All%20The%20Features%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20will%20receive%20its%20first%20C-295%20transport%20aircraft%20today.%20The%20plane%20was%20made%20by%20Airbus%20at%20a%20facility%20in%20Seville.%20IAF%20Chief%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20VR%20Chaudhari%20will%20receive%20the%20aircraft%20on%20behalf%20of%20India%20in%20Spain.%20The%20C-295%20transport%20plane%20is%20part%20of%20the%202021%20contract%20that%20India%20signed%20for%2056%20such%20aircrafts.%20Of%20these%2056%20aircrafts%2C%2016%20will%20be%20made%20in%20Spain%20and%20the%20remaining%2040%20will%20be%20manufactured%20in%20Gujarat's%20Vadodara%20as%20part%20of%20the%20joint%20venture%20between%20Tata%20and%20Airbus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet's%20take%20a%20look%20at%205%20features%20of%20the%20C-295%20transport%20plane%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-%20C-295MW%20aircraft%20possess%20a%20capacity%20of%205-10%20tonnes%20(which%20means%20it%20can%20carry%20around%2070%20soldiers).%20The%20plane%20will%20replace%20the%20ageing%20Avro%20aircraft%20of%20the%20IAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-%20For%20quick%20reaction%20and%20para-dropping%20troops%20and%20cargo%2C%20the%20aircraft%20also%20carries%20a%20rear%20ramp%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-%20An%20indigenous%20electronic%20warfare%20suite%20will%20be%20installed%20in%20all%2056%20aircraft%20in%20this%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-%20The%20inclusion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F%E2%80%8Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fndtv.in%2Findia%2Fair-force-will-get-its-first-c-295-aircraft-on-wednesday-4383882%5C%22%3EC-295%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20strengthen%20the%20air%20force%2C%20as%20the%20transport%20plane%20possesses%20the%20ability%20to%20land%20and%20take%20off%20even%20on%20short%20runways.%20The%20aircraft%20will%20require%20670%20meters%20of%20runway%20for%20take-off%20and%20only%20320%20meters%20for%20landing.%20This%20feature%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20the%20C-295%20to%20deliver%20essential%20goods%20in%20inaccessible%20and%20hilly%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-%20The%20C-295%20can%20fly%20for%20around%2011%20hours%20at%20a%20speed%20of%20about%20480%20kilometres%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESixteen%20of%20these%20aircraft%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20delivered%20within%2048%20months%20from%20Spain.%20The%20rest%20will%20be%20manufactured%20within%2010%20years%20of%20the%20contract%20signing%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fiaf-chief-vr-chaudhari-in-spain-this-week-to-receive-1st-c-295-transport-plane-for-india-4377670%5C%22%3Efirst%20project%20where%20military%20aircraft%20will%20be%20built%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20programme%20will%20boost%20the%20government's%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%20Abhiyan.%20The%20contract%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20reduce%20the%20import%20dependency%20by%20increasing%20domestic%20aviation%20manufacturing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694591280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fo4093sdo_c295-aircraft_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-s-first-c-295-transport-plane-to-be-delivered-today-all-you-need-to-know-about-it-4385321%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20will%20receive%20its%20first%20C-295%20transport%20aircraft%20today.%20The%20plane%20was%20made%20by%20Airbus%20at%20a%20facility%20in%20Seville.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-s-first-c-295-transport-plane-to-be-delivered-today-all-