e%20world%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20producer%20of%20opium%2C%20illicit%20drug%20manufacturing%20units%20where%20heroin%20is%20processed%20are%20aplenty%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Northeast.%20Manipur%2C%20Mizoram%20and%20Nagaland%2C%20among%20the%20easternmost%20states%2C%20are%20heavily%20engaged%20in%20the%20trafficking%20of%20ephedrine%20precursors%20for%20the%20manufacture%20of%20amphetamines%20and%20opioid%20analgesics%20like%20codeine%20and%20dextropropoxyphene%20for%20neighbouring%20countries.%20Lamenting%20the%20rampancy%20of%20drugs%20in%20the%20region%2C%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20stringent%20activist%20Binalakshmi%20Nepram%20says%20that%20the%20conventional%20Golden%20Triangle%20has%20expanded%20into%20a%20%E2%80%9CGolden%20Pentagon%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20induction%20of%20Vietnam-Cambodia%20and%20Mizoram-Manipur-Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECases%20of%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20with%20links%20to%20transnational%20organised%20criminals%20diversifying%20into%20the%20production%20of%20synthetic%20drugs%2C%20misusing%20licences%20to%20manufacture%20Tramadol%20painkiller%20tablets%20and%20codeine%20cough%20syrups%20for%20non-medical%20purposes%2C%20has%20added%20further%20complexity%20to%20the%20trafficking%20nexus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quantum%20of%20drugs%20smuggled%20via%20couriers%2C%20parcels%20and%20postal%20services%2C%20though%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20a%20few%20grams%20per%20package%20to%20avoid%20suspicion%2C%20has%20quadrupled%20since%202019%2C%20coinciding%20with%20increased%20Dark%20Web%20activity%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20seizure%20of%20300%20kg%20of%20cocaine%20from%20Tuticorin%20Port%20in%20April%202021%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%2C%20the%20frequency%20of%20cocaine%20consignments%20into%20India%20is%20yet%20another%20unsettling%20detail.%20The%20recent%20recovery%20of%203%20kg%20of%20%E2%80%98black%20cocaine%E2%80%99%2C%20at%20Ahmedabad%20airport%20was%20the%20DRI%E2%80%99s%20first%20seizure%20