%20than%201%2C44%2C000%20kg%20of%20drugs%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20through%20video-conferencing%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20pitched%20for%20%E2%80%9Cconfiscation%20of%20assets%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20strong%20deterrent%2C%20at%20a%20conference%20on%20%E2%80%98Drug%20Smuggling%20and%20National%20security%E2%80%99%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20strengthening%20law%20enforcement%20capacity%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20offering%20access%20to%20de-addiction%20treatment.%20There%20are%20535%20de-addiction%20centres%20unevenly%20distributed%20across%20India.%20As%20per%20the%20recent%20parliamentary%20panel%E2%80%99s%20report%20as%20many%20as%206.97%20lakh%20children%20(10-17%20years)%20are%20hooked%20on%20drugs%20in%20Punjab%2C%20and%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20there%20are%205%20lakh%20opioid%20addicts.%20If%20one%20considers%20just%20these%20two%20states%2C%20the%20requisite%20number%20of%20de-addiction%20centres%20is%20flagrantly%20low.%20Under%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENasha%20Mukt%20Bharat%20Abhiyaan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0it%20was%20proposed%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fd37a0157-40b9-4554-b161-c1616b1bc253%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fd37a0157-40b9-4554-b161-c1616b1bc253%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1694658845901000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0zgy9y5EXZhSAKCtT4EzdF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E290%20District%20De-addiction%20Centres%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0would%20be%20set%20up%20in%20vulnerable%20districts%2C%20a%20plan%20that%20is%20yet%20to%20fructify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20proposition%20to%20deal%20with%20substance%20abuse%20must%20begin%20with%20a%20forthright%20assessment%20of%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20problem.%20Trends%20such%20as%20the%20increasing%20use%20of%20methamphetamine%20must%20be%20taken%20into%20account.%20The%20number%20of%20women%20addicted%20to%20drugs%20is%20rising%20alarmingly%20in%20states%20that%20already%20register%20high%20substance%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20problem%20has%20captured%20national%20attention.%20Nevertheless%20discerning%20the%20deleterious%20effects%20of%20narcotics%20trafficking%20on%20a%20national%20scale%20is%20a%20formidable%20task.%20The%20complexity%20arises%20from%20the%20expansion%20and%20rising%20proportions%20of%20the%20drug%20influx%2C%20the%20environment%20within%20which%20it%20has%20succeeded%20in%20operating%2C%20the%20criminal-terror%20nexus%20that%20it%20has%20stimulated%20and%20the%20resultant%20social%20pathologies.%20A%20comprehensive%20counter-narcotics%20effort%20must%20perceive%20both%20a%20long-term%20strategic%20approach%20to%20disrupt%20trafficking%20and%20tackle%20the%20most%20salient%20public%20health%20challenges%20posed%20by%20illicit%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVaishali%20Basu%20Sharma%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eis%20an%20analyst%20on%20strategic%20and%20economic%20affairs.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694574627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13083908%2Fsyringe-1884784_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fin-combating-drug-trafficking-knowing-the-enemy-is-the-first-step%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20countrywide%20assessment%20to%20estimate%20the%20extent%20of%20substance%20abuse%20is%20long%20overdue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fin-combating-drug-trafficking-knowing-the-enemy-is-the-first-step%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Libya%20floods%3A%20Flooded%20city%20buries%20its%20dead%20in%20mass%20graves%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694574468000%2C%22visual%22%3A