0the%20prosecution%20story%20of%20how%20a%20private%20minority%20institution%20in%20Damoh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20has%20a%20uniform%20of%20shalwar-qameez%20and%20hijab%20for%20girls%20students%2C%20and%20non-Muslim%20students%20are%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20put%20tilak%20and%20tie%20%3Cem%3Ekalawa%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Urdu%20is%20being%20taught%20as%20a%20compulsory%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20non-Muslim%20students%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fdamoh-ganga-jamna-school-worried-hindu-parents-speak-up%5C%22%3Edenied%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20religious%20symbols%20being%20forced%20on%20their%20children.%20Be%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20the%20news%20spread%20like%20wildfire.%20The%20initial%20probe%20cleared%20the%20school%20from%20allegations%20of%20forcing%20Hindu%20students%20to%20wear%20hijab.%20A%20fresh%20probe%20was%20ordered%20by%20the%20home%20minister%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20state%20government%20promptly%20suspended%20the%20license%20of%20the%20private%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F26190454%2F2022_2img21_Feb_2022_PTI02_21_2022_000066B-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F26190454%2F2022_2img21_Feb_2022_PTI02_21_2022_000066B-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F26190454%2F2022_2img21_Feb_2022_PTI02_21_2022_000066B-1-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F26190454%2F2022_2img21_Feb_2022_PTI02_21_2022_000066B-1-1024x680.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-583811%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22797%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStudents%20stand%20outside%20a%20college%20as%20they%20boycott%20classes%20after%20being%20denied%20entry%20with%20hijab%20in%20the%20college%20premises%2C%20in%20Chikmagalur%2C%20on%20February%2021%2C%202022.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20publicly%20warned%20that%20any%20institution%20following%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20the%20Damoh%20school%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20run.%20The%20chief%20minister%20also%20registered%20his%20protest%20against%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fhijab-iqbal-madhya-pradesh-shivraj-singh-chouhan-polarising-politics-8664863%2F%5C%22%3Eteaching%3C%2Fa%3E%20poetry%20of%20a%20man%20who%20talked%20about%20the%20division%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%20(Dr.%20Muhammad%20Iqbal%2C%20the%20writer%20of%20S%3Cem%3Eare%20Jahan%20se%20Acha%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ELab%20pe%20aati%20hai%20dua%3C%2Fem%3E).%20A%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20under%20Sections%20295A%2C%20506%2C%20and%20120B%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20was%20registered.%20Provisions%20under%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Freedom%20of%20Religion%20Act%2C%202021%20alleging%20forced%20conversion%20of%20Hindu%20students%20were%20also%20invoked.%20Three%20people%20including%20the%20principal%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20typical%20%E2%80%98new%20India%E2%80%99%20fashion%2C%20parts%20of%20the%20school%2C%20the%20only%20English%20medium%20school%20in%20the%20area%20catering%20to%20around%201%2C200%20students%20from%20modest%20backgrounds%2C%20were%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fparts-of-madhya-pradesh-school-to-be-razed-hijab-controversy-district-education-minister-report-2393417-2023-06-15%5C%22%3Edemolished%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Last%20month%2C%20applicants%2C%20the%20principal%20along%20with%20the%20other%20two%20arrested%2C%20approached%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20high%20court%20for%20bail.%20The%20high%20court%20granted%20bail%20while%20imposing%20certain%20conditions%20to%20be%20strictly%20followed%20by%20the%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20high%20court%20directed%20the%20applicants%20to%20not%20prevent%20non-Muslim%20students%20from%20%E2%80%9Cwearing%20the%20essentials%20of%20their%20own%20religion%20as%20such%20wearing%20a%20sacred%20thread%20(%3Cem%3Ekalawa%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20putting%20tilak%20on%20the%20forehead%E2%80%9D.%20The%20court%2C%20recording%20the%20argument%20of%20the%20state%20that%20non-Muslim%20students%20cannot%20be%20compelled%20to%20read%20Urdu%2C%20further%20directed%20the%20applicants%20to%20not%20compel%20the%20non-Muslim%20students%20to%20read%2Fstudy%20any%20language%20which%20has%20not%20been%20prescribed%20by%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20education%20board%20and%20impart%20only%20%E2%80%9Cmodern%20education%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20accepting%20this%20submission%20can%20be%20criticised%20on%20several%20grounds%2C%20one%20among%20them%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20Urdu%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20is%20a%20recognised%20language%20under%20the%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(Madhya%20Pradesh)%20Regulations%2C%201965.%20Lastly%2C%20the%20applicants%20were%20strictly%20directed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgirl%20students%20of%20other%20religion%20i.e.%20Hindu%20and%20Jain%20etc.%20shall%20not%20be%20compelled%20to%20wear%20head%20scarf%20(Hijaab)%20anywhere%20in%20the%20school%20premises%20or%20in%20the%20classrooms%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hijab%20matter%20before%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%2C%20the%20government%20order%20(GO)%20dated%20February%205%2C%202022%2C%20upheld%20by%20the%20court%2C%20reads%20that%20where%20the%20uniform%20in%20question%20is%20that%20of%20a%20private%20school%2C%20the%20uniform%20shall%20be%20decided%20upon%20by%20the%20school%20management.%20This%20reading%20of%20the%20GO%20was%20accepted%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20its%20judgment%20by%20both%20Justice%20Gupta%20and%20Justice%20Dhulia%2C%20with%20one%20upholding%20the%20GO%20and%20the%20other%20quashing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fhijab-ban-karnataka-zealtory-judicial-illogic%5C%22%3EHijab%20Ban%3A%20The%20Marriage%20of%20Convenience%20Between%20Zealotry%20and%20Judicial%20Illogic%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20more%20case%20that%20requires%20a%20mention%20here%20is%20from%20Kerala.%20In%202018%2C%20when%20Muslim%20girls%20approached%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%20against%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20wear%20a%20hijab%20in%20a%20Christian%20minority%20institution%2C%20the%20court%20was%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccommunity%20rights%20of%20a%20minority%20institution%20override%20the%20individual%20rights%20of%20students%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20hijab%20matter%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%2C%20while%20distinguishing%20the%20judgment%20on%20facts%2C%20recorded%20agreement%20with%20the%20ratio%20of%20this%20Kerala%20high%20court%20judgment.%20It%20is%20relevant%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20the%20Damoh%20School%20is%20a%20private%20minority%20institution%20and%20the%20uniform%20was%20prescribed%20by%20the%20school%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20latter%20part%20of%202021%20and%202022%20witnessed%20strong%20protests%20by%20young%20Muslim%20women%20and%20the%20Muslim%20community%20at%20large%20against%20the%20restriction%20on%20hijab.%20With%20the%20state%20government%20and%20judiciary%20supporting%20the%20restriction%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Karnataka%20witnessed%20a%20steep%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fpucl-releases-report-on-impact-of-hijab-ban-on-muslim-girl-students-in-karnataka-8371485%2F%5C%22%3Edropout%20rate%20of%20Muslim%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20government%20institutions%20and%20pre-university%20colleges.%20Those%20who%20could%20afford%2C%20opted%20for%20private%20institutions%20to%20continue%20their%20studies%2C%20others%20vanished%20from%20the%20face%20of%20educational%20statistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20remained%20floating%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20such%20a%20prohibition%3A%20the%20idea%20of%20uniformity.%20The%20exclusion%20of%20religious%20symbols%20from%20educational%20institutions.%20This%20reasoning%20was%20even%20bought%20by%20some%20of%20our%20liberal%20allies.%20This%20very%20%E2%80%98reasoning%E2%80%99%20falls%20flat%20with%20the%20Damoh%20case.%20The%20series%20of%20incidents%2C%20the%20employment%20of%20all%20judicial%20and%20extrajudicial%20methods%20to%20create%20a%20precedent%20against%20the%20school%20in%20Damoh%2C%20and%20the%20subsequent%20conditions%20imposed%20through%20the%20bail%20order%2C%20only%20reinforce%20what%20has%20been%20argued%20for%20long%20by%20those%20who%20are%20direct%20victims%20of%20this%20identity%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20the%20discrepancies%20between%20the%20stories%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20there%20is%20one%20lesson%20that%20is%20consistent%3A%20a%20%E2%80%98Hindu%E2%80%99%20must%20not%20be%20prevented%20from%20wearing%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekalawa%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20putting%20a%20%3Cem%3Etilak%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20%E2%80%98Hindu%E2%80%99%20must%20not%20be%20told%20what%20to%20wear.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20it%20for%20%E2%80%9Cour%20people%E2%80%9D.%20We%20cannot%20be%20told%20not%20to%20follow%20%E2%80%9Cour%20faith%E2%80%9D%20in%20%E2%80%9Cour%20country%E2%80%9D.%20The%20disgust%20towards%20a%20language%20that%20is%20regarded%20as%20Muslim.%20This%20is%20what%20it%20is.%20This%20is%20what%20it%20has%20always%20been.%20The%20Damoh%20story%20is%20an%20Indian%20story.%20It%20is%20another%20testament%20of%20something%20overt%20that%20the%20people%20at%20the%20margins%20always%20knew.%20It%20is%20either%20our%20blindness%20or%20our%20cowardice%20to%20not%20see%20the%20obvious.%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENabeela%20Jamil%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20lawyer.%20She%20assisted%20on%20the%20Hijab%20matter%20from%20the%20Petitioner%E2%80%99s%20side%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694572219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F26175827%2Fhijab-poster.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftwo-hijab-cases-one-lesson%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20all%20the%20discrepancies%20between%20the%20stories%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20there%20is%20one%20thing%20that%20is%20consistent%2C%20which%20is%20to%20impose%20on%20people%20at%20the%20margins%20an%20idea%20of%20'uniformity'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftwo-hijab-cases-one-lesson%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple's%20New%20iPhones%20Get%20New%20Charging%20Systems%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20showcase%20at%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20headquarters%20in%20Cupertino%2C%20California%2C%20comes%20as%20the%20company%20tries%20to%20reverse%20a%20mild%20slump%20that%20has%20seen%20its%20sales%20drop.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694572145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F65011d7925000051005e8633.jpeg%3Fcache%3Dvl9mqu8ni6%26ops%3D224_126%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fapple-event_n_65011c75e4b01f6f9b9b606d%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20showcase%20at%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20headquarters%20in%20Cupertino%2C%20California%2C%20comes%20as%20the%20company%20tries%20to%20reverse%20a%20mild%20slump%20that%20has%20seen%20its%20sales%20drop.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fapple-event_n_65011c75e4b01f6f9b9b606d%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentr