%20plot%20of%20land%20has%20paddy%2C%20fruit%20trees%2C%20spices%2C%20herbs%20and%20even%20flowering%20plants%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Keyur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EKeyur%20pitches%20in%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20so%20much%20space%20to%20move%20around%2C%20and%20we%20were%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20world.%20We%20even%20bartered%20rice%20for%20vegetables%20grown%20on%20the%20farm!%20After%20three%20months%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20what%20we%20had%20was%20gold.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hamlet%2C%20which%20was%20once%20occupied%20by%20Girdhar%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20is%20now%20converted%20into%20the%20improved%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F256646%2Futtarakhand-kumaon-ecofriendly-travel-destination-sustainable-homestay-organic-farm-solar-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresidential%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20farm.%20The%20Barad%20brothers%20say%20that%20all%20they%20did%20was%20extend%20the%20bedrooms%2C%20add%20a%2070-ft%20verandah%20and%20make%20harmonious%20cosmetic%20changes%20to%20marry%20the%20inside%20and%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20bungalow%20in%20the%202022%20monsoons.%20Among%20delays%20in%20receiving%20material%20due%20to%20the%20rains%2C%20we%20also%20experienced%20frequent%20electricity%20cuts.%20I%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20overseeing%20the%20site%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nishit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20three%20years%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329447%2Fdevra-homestay-in-udaipur-barren-land-to-heritage-property%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erigorous%20effort%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20toil%2C%20it%20was%20worth%20it.%20Though%20accustomed%20to%20luxuries%20such%20as%20air%20conditioners%20and%20geysers%20back%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20brothers%20shar