ndia.com%2F322666%2Fretired-couple-turns-ancestral-land-into-eco-friendly-konkan-homestay-sindhudurg-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20interspersed%20valleys%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20honey-coloured%20villages%20amidst%20the%20desert%20sands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20a%20shame%20not%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20this%20scene.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20one%20such%20road%20trip%20in%201994%2C%20Major%20Durga%20Das%20and%20his%20wife%20Jyoti%20Jasol%2C%20succumbed%20to%20the%20same%20fate.%20Fondly%20called%20%E2%80%98Major%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20once%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20in%20Udaipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Jyoti%20(57)%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20royal%20ancestral%20line%20of%20the%20Rathores%20of%20Marwar-Jodhpur.%20Major%20(66)%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20a%20descendant%20of%20the%20royal%20ancestral%20lines%20of%20The%20House%20of%20Bassi-Udaipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20look%20at%20the%20scenery%2C%20the%20couple%20recalls%2C%20was%20all%20it%20took%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20buy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284474%2Fhow-couple-quit-city-life-to-build-sustainable-homestay-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%202.5%20acre%20land%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Jyoti%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20was%20still%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20and%20I%20was%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20Textile%20Gallery%20at%20the%20City%20Palace.%20But%20we%20both%20had%20a%20nagging%20thought%20that%20our%20lives%20were%20not%20being%20used%20creatively.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20after%2013%20years%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20my%20husband%20left%20the%20service%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20start%20developing%20this%20land%20we%20had%20bought%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Devra%E2%80%99%2C%20by%20which%20they%20christened%20this%20plot%2C%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20local%20name%20given%20to%20tribal%20temples.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20Army%2C%20Major%20says%20his%20guiding%20belief%20has%20always%20centred%20around%20serving%20both%20the%20nation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300372%2F8-pocket-friendly-cosy-homestays-in-the-mountains-for-that-scenic-winter-break%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20this%20(Devra)%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20cultivate%20a%20generation%20that%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20their%20surroundings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98What%20is%20stopping%20you%20from%20making%20the%20dream%20come%20true%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202229px)%20100vw%2C%202229px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20Devra%20the%20local%20women%20of%20Udaipur%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20showcase%20their%20skills%20while%20earning%20a%20livelihood%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749.jpg%202229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329449%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221486%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20Devra%20the%20local%20women%20of%20Udaipur%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20showcase%20their%20skills%20while%20earning%20a%20livelihood%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Jyoti%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20first%20began%20working%20out%20of%20this%20land%2C%20they%20started%20floriculture%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20supplying%20flowers%20to%20the%20Taj%20Palace%2C%20Udaipur.%20However%2C%20what%20they%20estimated%20to%20be%20a%20booming%20business%20did%20not%20work%20out.%20They%20had%20hit%20a%20dead%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20couple%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20in%201997%2C%20where%20their%20baby%20girl%20was%20born%2C%20and%20Jyoti%20spent%20the%20next%20two%20years%20being%20a%20doting%20mother.%20But%20the%20dream%20she%20harboured%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F258991%2Fcouple-quits-city-life-eco-friendly-homestay-banyan-bliss-ethnic-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Udaipur%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20being%20silenced.%20%E2%80%9CIn%201999%2C%20I%20decided%20there%20was%20no%20better%20time%20than%20the%20present%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20land%20and%20this%20time%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20plan.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202004%2C%20when%20Devra%20officially%20started%20welcoming%20guests%2C%20Jyoti%20would%20make%20frequent%20trips%20between%20Delhi%2C%20where%20her%20husband%20and%20child%20were%2C%20and%20Udaipur%2C%20where%20her%20dream%20was.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20years%20were%20beautiful%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20journey%20of%20inking%20relationships%20with%20the%20craftsmen%20of%20the%20city%2C%20since%20architects%20and%20civil%20engineers%20were%20tough%20to%20find%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20got%20a%20local%20person%2C%20Shivji%2C%20on%20board%2C%20and%20he%20helped%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280532%2Fchildhood-friends-convert-grandmothers-house-into-eco-friendly-homestay-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20the%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20what%20it%20is%20today.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20Shivji%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Rupa%20%3Cem%3EBai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(an%20honorific%20to%20describe%20a%20woman)%2C%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20staff%20at%20Devra.%20She%20has%20witnessed%20the%20evolution%20of%20both%20the%20homestay%2C%20and%20the%20city%2C%20through%20these%20years%20and%20calls%20it%20a%20privilege.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20progress%20of%20our%20family%2C%20and%20of%20Devra%2C%20is%20inseparable.%20We%20have%20watched%20our%20children%20grow%20alongside%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20memories%20of%20their%20early%20years%20are%20woven%20into%20every%20brick%20and%20corner%20that%20my%20husband%20assembled%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rupa%20Bai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20Jyoti%20has%20enjoyed%20Rupa%20Bai%E2%80%99s%20company%20among%20the%20many%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeautiful%20connections%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20cemented.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20journey%20taught%20me%20to%20be%20patient%20and%20take%20things%20as%20they%20come.%20Everything%20happens%20in%20its%20own%20space%20and%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202229px)%20100vw%2C%202229px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Devra%20prides%20itself%20on%20traditional%20Udaipur%20culture%20and%20authentic%20delicacies%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819.jpg%202229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7369-1_11zon-1694171819-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329450%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221486%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDevra%20prides%20itself%20on%20traditional%20Udaipur%20culture%20and%20authentic%20delicacies%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Jyoti%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20guests%20at%20the%20housewarming%20lunch%20in%202004%20included%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20parents%20and%20all%20the%20craftsmen%20who%20had%20been%20a%20part%20of%20their%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20the%20assurance%20that%20even%20if%20I%20want%20to%20make%2010%20more%20houses%2C%20these%20people%20will%20support%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jyoti%20adds%2C%20laughing.%20Such%20is%20the%20strength%20of%20their%20bond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20majesty%20of%20Udaipur%E2%80%99s%20lands%20comes%20alive%20with%20this%20property%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20with%20three%20rooms%20is%20now%20a%2010-bedroom%20heritage%20homestay%20made%20of%20Rajasthani%20stone%2C%20bang%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20lush%20fields%20and%20farms.%20However%2C%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20state%20of%20the%20land%20in%201994.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20visited%20the%20land%20for%20the%20first%20time%20all%20we%20saw%20was%20cactus.%20The%20land%20did%20not%20support%20the%20growth%20of%20anything%20else.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20a%20solution%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298965%2Fdelhi-professiors-turn-traditional-houses-into-homestays-boost-sustainable-tourism-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransform%20the%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20viable%20farm%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Pichola%20Lake%20in%20Udaipur.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20bringing%20in%20soil%20from%20the%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20While%20Jyoti%20succeeded%20in%20doing%20this%20at%20the%20time%2C%20today%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Lake%20Protection%20and%20Conservation%20Authority%20passed%20a%20proposal%20that%20put%20three%20lakes%20in%20Udaipur%20under%20a%20prohibited%20zone%2C%20thus%20curbing%20desilting%20or%20soil%20extraction%20activities%20in%20them.%20Pichola%20Lake%20was%20one%20of%20these.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C20%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20ban%20that%20now%20exists%20over%20removing%20soil%20from%20the%20lake%20was%20not%20there.%20So%2C%20when%20the%20lake%20would%20dry%20up%20in%20summer%20up%20to%20its%20middle%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20quality%20loamy%20soil%20would%20be%20left%20behind.%20This%20soil%2C%20filled%20with%20minerals%20and%20nutrients%2C%20is%20perfect%20for%20growing%20plants.%20We%20started%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20land%20to%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311053%2Fdushyant-vashisht-turned-cottage-to-sustainable-homestay-bir-terraces-uttarakhand-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20first%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20Devra%20guests%20are%20taken%20to%20experience%20the%20local%20culture%20and%20the%20nearby%20villages%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329479%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20Devra%20guests%20are%20taken%20to%20experience%20the%20local%20culture%20and%20the%20nearby%20villages%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Jyoti%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20dish%20prepared%20at%20the%20homestay%20is%20from%20the%20fresh%20produce%20grown%20on%20the%20land.%20%E2%80%9CWheat%2C%20seasonal%20vegetables%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emethi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eavlas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20berries%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejamuns%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20guavas%2C%20chikoos%2C%20neem%2C%20tamarind%2C%20date%E2%80%A6%20You%20name%20it%20and%20we%20grow%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Jyoti%20proudly%20stating%20that%20there%20are%20trees%20of%20every%20variety%20here%20and%20adding%20they%20harvest%20400%20kg%20of%20chikoos%20every%20year%20along%20with%20other%20fruits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeeping%20up%20with%20traditional%20practices%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Echulha%3C%2Fem%3E%20cooking%20method%20(cooking%20in%20an%20earthen%20pot%20to%20retain%20the%20moisture%20and%20aroma%20of%20the%20food)%20that%20the%20family%20has%20been%20following%20for%2025%20years%20now%20lends%20an%20authentic%20flavour%20to%20the%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20whether%20it%20is%20%3Cem%3Elal%20maas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traditional%20Rajasthani%20red%20meat%20curry)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebhuta%20ki%20subji%3C%2Fem%3E%20(corn%20vegetable)%2C%20%3Cem%3Etarbuz%20ki%20subji%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20vegetable%20made%20with%20watermelon%20crust)%2C%20%3Cem%3Emint%20lauki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bottle%20gourd%20and%20mint%20juice)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emakki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(corn)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20chulha%20rotis%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20with%20love%20by%20Rupa%20Bai%2C%20every%20dish%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90205%2F10-sustainable-homestays-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearthy%20notes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%20is%20that%20you%20could%20learn%20to%20cook%20this%20feast%20yourself%20at%20the%20Heritage%20Cooking%20Class%20hosted%20by%20Jyoti.%20Credit%20her%20for%20being%20a%2