%20and%20Sustainability%E2%80%99.%20It%20will%20take%20place%20from%2019%20and%C2%A0%2020%20September%202023%20at%20India%20Habitat%20Centre%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20conference%20will%20bring%20together%20professionals%2C%20educators%2C%20leaders%2C%20policymakers%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20students%20to%20collaborate%20on%20climate%20change%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20conference%20offers%20an%20exceptional%20opportunity%20for%20educators%2C%20researchers%2C%20policymakers%2C%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20to%20come%20together%20and%20exchange%20ideas%2C%20strategies%2C%20and%20innovative%20solutions%20for%20effectively%20addressing%20planetary%20issues%20of%20climate%20action%20and%20sustainability%20through%20education.%20We%20will%20be%20demonstrating%20what%20changes%20have%20been%20made%20through%20case%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20aim%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315625%2Fdelhi-meeta-sharma-gupta-shumee-sustainable-toy-brand-develop-cognitive-motor-skills-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20inspire%20and%20motivate%20young%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20pursue%20sustainable%20solutions%20through%20success%20stories%20and%20case%20examples.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CYouth%20play%20a%20critical%20role%2C%20both%20today%20and%20tomorrow%2C%20in%20many%20of%20the%20sustainable%20development%20goals.%20Whether%20it%20is%20the%20SDG%20related%20to%20hunger%2C%20quality%20education%2C%20gender%20equality%2C%20decent%20work%20and%20economic%20growth%2C%20or%20reduced%20inequalities%2C%20all%20these%20changes%20start%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CYOUTH%E2%80%9D.%20We%20tend%20to%20follow%20what%20the%20Youth%C2%A0%20does%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20%3Cstrong%3EPradip%20Burman%2C%20Chairman%2C%20Mobius%20Foundation.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICSE%202023%20chief%20guest%20is%20%3Cstrong%3EEducation%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20who%20will%20be%20inaugurating%C2%A0%20the%20conference.%20Other%20notable%20attendees%20include%20Dr%20Anil%20Prakash%20Joshi%20%E2%80%94%20environmentalist%2C%20green%20activist%20and%20founder%20of%20Himalayan%20Environmental%20Studies%20and%20Conservation%20Organization%20(HESCO)%3B%20and%20Jadav%20%E2%80%9CMolai%E2%80%9D%20Payeng%20%E2%80%94%20environmental%20activist%2C%20forestry%20worker%2C%20renowned%20as%20the%20Forest%20Man%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIncluding%20sustainability%20in%20national%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius1-1694094245.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ICSE%202023%20will%20focus%20on%20educating%20for%20climate%20change%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius1-1694094245.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius1-1694094245-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius1-1694094245-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius1-1694094245-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius1-1694094245-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329405%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EICSE%202023%20will%20focus%20on%20educating%20for%20climate%20change%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20to%20reform%20the%20national%20education%20framework%20and%20curriculum.%20This%20aligns%20with%20the%20goals%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A