%20hers%20to%20roam%20through%20the%20area%20and%20keep%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324744%2Fmany-nayak-historic-film-on-caste-kahi-debe-sandesh-created-chhatisgarhi-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrack%20of%20happenings.%3C%2Fa%3E%20She%20did%20this%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20woman%20with%20a%20mental%20disability.%20She%20would%20observe%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%E2%80%99s%20movements%20and%20then%20report%20these%20to%20the%20Mukti%20Bahini%2C%20who%20would%20then%20act%20on%20these%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Sitara%20Begum%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20served%20as%20a%20doctor%20with%20the%20force.%20The%20Kolkata%20native%20oversaw%20operations%20at%20a%20Bangladesh%20Hospital%20where%20casualties%20of%20war%20and%20emergent%20cases%20needed%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20before%20these%20two%20fearless%20women%20could%20play%20their%20role%2C%20a%20young%20girl%20Rajkumari%20Gupta%20displayed%20the%20same%20zeal%20during%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324194%2Fkishori-mohan-bandyopadhyay-worked-with-ronald-ross-malaria-research-nobel-prize-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20struggle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20and%20her%20husband%20Madan%20Mohan%20Gupta%20joined%20the%20Independence%20movement%20where%20they%20would%20deliver%20secret%20messages%20to%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20times%2C%20Gupta%20put%20her%20life%20on%20the%20line%20while%20delivering%20guns%20to%20the%20revolutionaries.%20She%20once%20famously%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHum%20upar%20se%20Gandhivaadi%20the%2C%20neeche%20se%20krantivaadi%20the%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(We%20were%20Gandhians%20from%20above%3B%20underneath%20we%20were%20revolutionaries).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%