0could%20build%20a%20career%20in%20the%20topic%20she%20taught.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20studied%20microbiology%2C%20I%20already%20knew%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20mushroom%20cultivation.%20This%20seemed%20a%20better%20idea%20for%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202017%2C%20she%20set%20up%20her%20company%20Natural%20Bio%20Impact%20and%20Research%20Pvt%20Ltd%20to%20grow%20mushrooms.%20With%20Rs%203%2C000%2C%20she%20bought%2010%20kg%20of%20oyster%20mushroom%20spawns%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296981%2Fbihar-homemaker-turns-entrepreneur-with-mushroom-farming-at-home-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivated%20mushrooms%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20her%20home%20in%20a%2010%C3%9710%20sq%20ft%20room.%20But%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20her%20expectations%2C%20she%20could%20not%20get%20a%20good%20yield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20every%20kg%20of%20mushroom%20spawns%2C%20we%20should%20have%20gotten%20at%20least%2010%20kg%20of%20mushrooms.%20That%20means%2C%20in%20total%2C%20we%20should%20have%20gotten%20100%20kg%20of%20produce.%20But%20our%20yield%20was%2030%20percent%20less%20than%20anticipated%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNidhi-Katare-2-1694005146.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi%20grows%20Pleurotus%20Florida%20oyster%20mushrooms%20which%20are%20known%20for%20their%20medicinal%20properties.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNidhi-Katare-2-1694005146.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNidhi-Katare-2-1694005146-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNidhi-