and%20always%20motivated%20me%20in%20this%20journey.%20There%20have%20been%20times%20when%20I%20lost%20hope%2C%20but%20he%20always%20encouraged%20me.%20He%20even%20quit%20his%20job%20at%20Reliance%20as%20a%20branch%20manager%20to%20support%20me%20in%20marketing%20and%20expanding%20the%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20husband%2C%20Sanjay%20Katare%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20from%20scratch.%20We%20knew%20that%20these%20mushrooms%20were%20in%20great%20demand%20by%20pharmaceutical%20companies%2C%20but%20we%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20market%20the%20products%20to%20the%20right%20people.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20even%20went%20door-to-door%20to%20sell%20our%20oyster%20mushrooms%20to%20traders%20in%20the%20Delhi%20market.%20Today%2C%20we%20sell%20our%20products%20across%20India%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Surat%20and%20Kutch%20among%20other%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20job%20to%20support%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20business%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20very%20risky%20decision%20as%20we%20both%20did%20not%20have%20jobs%2C%20and%20we%20had%20a%20small%20son%20to%20take%20care%20of.%20There%20were%20even%20times%20when%20we%20thought%20of%20quitting%20this%20business%20and%20returning%20to%20our%20private%20jobs%20as%20we%20were%20not%20getting%20good%20profits%20because%20of%20low%20yields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20their%20perseverance%20paid%20off%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20a%20good%20boost%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290624%2Fmba-graduate-starts-mushroom-farming-during-lockdown-now-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%20when